005500171119<install_instructions><![CDATA[
005600171119     *----------------------------------------------------------------      ------
005700171119     *  1. Upload entire XML to your AS/400 to a source file 112 long, into any mbr
005800171119     *     name not in this XML (suggest member name like ABCX or XYZX). The source
005900171119     *     file must be in the library where source and objects are to be installed.
006000171119     *
006100171119     *  2. If you have XMLPREVIEW installed, skip to step 3.
006200171119     *
006300171119     *     Copy the text between the start tag <install_program> and the end
006400171119     *     tag </install_program> into any member name (your choice)
006500171119     *     in file QRPGLESRC member type RPGLE.   CRTBNDRPG to compile.
006600171119     *     NOTE: You need extract the install program only once, this same program
006700171119     *           will install any upload on this page.
006800171119     *
006900171119     *  3. Call the install program (or execute XmlPrevew) passing these 3 parms.
007000171119     *       'your-member-name you uploaded this text into'
007100171119     *       'your-source-file-name the member is in'
007200171119     *       'your-library-name the source file is in'
007300171119     *
007400171119     *  The various source members will be extracted and the objects required
007500171119     *   for the application will be created in your-library-name.
007600171119     *----------------------------------------------------------------      ------
007700171119]]>  </install_instructions>
