202700171119:XH3.Search and replace (VALUES)
202800171119:P.
202900171119Specify the argument you want to search for. The second value
203000171119specifies the replacement string.
203100171119:P.
203200171119Use quotes to specify empty strings or strings with preceding or
203300171119trailing spaces.
203400171119:P.
203500171119Specify hexadecimal values as x'..', e.g. x'A3'.
203600171119:P.
203700171119:HP2.Search argument.:EHP2. Type the string you want to search
203800171119for, enclosed in single quotation marks. The string can be character
203900171119or hexadecimal.
204000171119:P.
